IN THE CIRCUIT COURT OF THE FIFTEENTH JUDICIAL CIRCUIT IN AND FOR PALM BEACH COUNTY, FLORIDA (CRIMINAL DIVISION)
STATE'S ATTORNEY SUBPOENA TO: JUAN P. ALESSI 6791 FAIRWAY LAKES DRIVE BOYNTON BEACH, FL 33437-6802
GREETINGS:
YOU ARE HEREBY COMMANDED TO BE AND APPEAR BEFORE THE STATE'S ATTORNEY or his assistant, in and for Palm Beach County, Florida, at the Criminal Justice Building, 401 North Dixie Highway, West Palm Beach, Florida, on WEDNESDAY, the 23RD day of NOVEMBER, 2005, at 10:00A.M., for interrogation and the truth to speak, in a certain matter pending and under investigation. Failure to appear will subject you to contempt of Court.
(Circuit Court Seal)
DALIAH M. WEISS Assistant State Attorney
WITNESS my hand and the seal of this Court on 16 day of NOVEMBER 2005.
SHARON R. BOCK, Clerk
By Mercedes Ditrop Deputy Clerk
Received this subpoena on the 17 day of NOV 2005 , and executed the same on the 17 day of nov , 2005, by delivering a True Copy thereof to the within named witness in the County of Palm Beach, State of Florida.
SHERIFF, PALM BEACH COUNTY
By: Deputy Sheriff
SERVED TIME 2:15 PM DATE 11/17/05 COMMENT:
SERVING PROGRESS
Page 121 of 124 Public Records Request No.: 17-295
07/26/17 1:50.
